title: where is all my missions?
body:
I have made these 2017 worlds missions and after multiple ones, there is none others but just one. It's that one where you have to score (for me now) 34 points to unlock master pickem poro icon. Do i have to get this one done first before getting new missions or what? Kinda want to use my points but if there still is a chance to get that chroma and ward...
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}}

replies.body: You've completed them!  New missions for Worlds refresh each week in alignment with Finals.  We're getting near the end here, so there may not be any left.  I'm sure more missions will be coming in the future, hang tight!
